The paper focuses on robotic manipulation, which is a core topic in robotics (cs.RO). The approach is based on deep generative models that learn to imagine plausible images from data, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves planning and control, which are key areas in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY).
